{"tid":945703,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[An] 天域永恆 新Game 幾爽 有D似三小俠","createTime":"2018-12-18T05:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T02:40:13.000Z","uid":48887,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb0051fcd21b445fa31168f9cf042b35b8afa42","tid":945703,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/PIaLWX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FPIaLWX.png&h=36bddb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的，話說前排小弟聽到話三小俠出手機板，本住想回憶下童年嘅我，梗係要去撚下啦，點知下載完真係hi出聲，想當年日玩夜玩嘅三小俠竟然完全變哂，個情景就好似明明買左包老母麵，打開入面竟然係咪咪麵！先唔話隻咪咪麵係咩味道先，可能因為真係期望愈大失望愈大，有種往日時光已不再嘅感覺，反倒有啲唔係幾開心咁唧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係機緣巧合之下，就喺google play入面搵到隻手機遊戲，個名叫做《天域永恆》，睇到啲玩法有啲似舊時三小嘅影子，就DL咗黎玩，雖然唔係咩大廠出品，但入到去係三小果一類畫面覺得OK啦，只係唔太習慣非三小俠嘅角色，但之後玩落其實係幾爽，講就唔係太有說服力，就俾啲打鬥圖俾您地望望喇。 （遊戲入面可以無限連技打一堆敵人嘅時候係幾爽吓）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/NXBwag.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FNXBwag.png&h=614ab8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/MCTlbf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FMCTlbf.png&h=cd20d50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/kVZHM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FkVZHM3.png&h=1e4ee3b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/18/RqoUvP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2FRqoUvP.png&h=8b662253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一款角色扮演的橫版戰鬥手機遊戲，基本操作其實同三小唔係差好多，只係絕招唔駛儲氣出，將技能簡單化左，即撳即有，可能有巴絲會話三小正好多，咁我都認同嘅，但無論點都好啦，唔計三小，其實呢隻細細地嘅手機遊戲，玩落都真係唔錯架！遊戲入面同一開始嘅三小差唔多，都係一角一職，入面有劍士，刺客同魔法師，玩法呀出招呀果啲，玩過三小俠嘅都應該好易上手架喇，我就唔多講。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，隻game話係由一本仙俠小說《天域蒼穹》改編而成，內容係乜？小弟都只係喺隻game度得知一小部份，要大家自己玩落去睇下點發展啦，除左打打殺殺之外，隻game入面仲有啲小遊戲可以俾大家挑戰下，有咩小遊戲？等各位巴絲自己DL黎試下撚，最重要嘅係遊戲入面會送幾多嘅遊戲資源俾玩家，唔太需要好似三小咁，狂刷材料升同轉職又或者需要瘋狂課金，得閒無事，坐車屙屎開黎撳下都相信係一個唔錯嘅選擇黎架！<br />\n<br />\n最後貼埋啲有用嘅link俾大家<br />\n<br />\nGoogle dl:<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lg.tycq.game980x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.lg.tycq.game980x&d=%2F8IpAWi2c54X29EX9Mi5WjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=bc291f2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lg.tycq.game980x</a><br />\n<br />\n官網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://dwz.cn/VzW75rgH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdwz.cn%2FVzW75rgH&d=%2F8IpAWi2c54X29EX9Mi5WjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6f4a931b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dwz.cn/VzW75rgH</a><br />\nfb專頁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yhgdmobile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyhgdmobile&d=%2F8IpAWi2c54X29EX9Mi5WjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=d53c8f8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yhgdmobile</a>"},{"pid":"f8cef57a8517f77432dd82621c59ee724cc7694f","tid":945703,"uid":13287,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:14:33.000Z","msg":"見到D傷害數字咁樣都唔想玩"},{"pid":"5d271057e3c2b03f8e4afd87ad9ae20ecb90c508","tid":945703,"uid":31425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"成個MON都係數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b337ae41c77d17f9c0ac0312fc59844907eade23","tid":945703,"uid":136312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d271057e3c2b03f8e4afd87ad9ae20ecb90c508","tid":945703,"uid":31425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re